name: IAM-05-3
description:
v4w.enko - "IAM-05-3" [Intermediate Algorithmic Multicomponent - 05-3]
"Voronoi diagram" cells based on "MetaBall" algorithm according to the subdivision of 44 curves to the 11 segments, are used to generate this "interactive flower". The cross-patterns transformation is applied in different levels of the algorithm and the only 1 layer is highlighted. Colored in special violet palette. 
The "crystal inside" is one more layer based on 8 charge points of main "Metaball" algorithm`s triggers connected by "Delaunay Triangulation" process. 
 Packed as GIF. 1024*1024px / 181 frames.
